# Install

- 2 servers
- add private interfaces
- update boxes
- install base packages
- install iptables rules
- setup iptables at boot

# Workers

- install virtualenvwrapper
- logout / login to get the WORKON_HOME ready
- install dev packages (make gcc python-dev)
- install python-software-properties (add-apt-repository)
- install zmq3
- create workers virtualenv
    - install ansible libzmq
- increase fileno
- build and deploy ansible packages

# API

- add nfs-kernel-server
- setup /etc/exports and folders + perms
- restart nfs-kernel-server service

# Graphite
- setup virtualenv `virtualenv /opt/ve/graphite`
- pip install soft
- fetch http://cairographics.org/pycairo/
- apt install pkg-config libcairo2-dev
- read README build use waf + http://stackoverflow.com/questions/11491268/install-pycairo-in-virtualenv
- in

